                            </footer>
                        </blockquote>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <div class="testimonial-card testimonial-card-featured">
                        <div class="testimonial-icon">
                            <i class="bi bi-quote"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="testimonial-image">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544717305-2782549b5136?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=300&h=300&q=80"
                                alt="Student portrait" class="img-fluid rounded-circle">
                        </div>
